                        <h1>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</h1>

                        <p>In 1989, newly formed Town Councils took over from HDB the responsibility of managing the common areas of HDB estates. Led by the elected Members of Parliament, and supported by community leaders and residents, the Town Council has policy-implementation and decision-making powers to effectively perform the estate management functions.</p>

