                        <div class="textContainer">
                            <p><strong>Roles and Duties of Bishan-Toa Payoh Town Council </strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Maintain the common areas outside the residential units but within the block, gardens, market & food centres, open spaces, shophouses and void decks.</li>
                                <li>Supervise cleaning and landscaping works.</li>
                                <li>Provide essential maintenance and lift rescue service (EMSU: 1800 241 7711).</li>
                                <li>Improve estate with new facilities, for example, childrens playgrounds, covered linkways and many others. </li>
                                <li>Control and manage the use of common areas, for example, social functions at void decks. </li>
                                <li>Engage residents in community-related activities, for example, Project VisionScroll, Tour of Toa Payoh Trail and Tree Planting Day. </li>
